CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, on December 27, 1969, reads: "DANDY DUFFERS PARTY - Gathered at the Club Loendi, in a recent social hour, were these members of the Dandy Duffers Golf and Country Club...."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Dandy Duffers Golf Club members including unknown man, Charles Berry, Dave Goggins, and Sterling Perkins, posed with trophies in Loendi Club, with sign reading "Dandy Duffers Inter - Club tournament trophies presented by Pepsi Cola"
